usethebotTitle: Use Lobby Bot to safely host lobbies
usethebotDescription: This bot is a protection against [[box-spawners]](<https://discord.com/channels/1000163670808068147/1000163671923765327/1201595194559184926>), rule-12-breaking hackers, and other problematic users, and is also a convenient way to share your lobby with other players.\nUse **/lobby** to share your code. \n[[More info + video guide]](<https://discord.com/channels/1000163670808068147/1000163671923765327/1139339639023476758>)
